OL,3,CShopper footfall down on last January
OL,4,Cbut up on disappointing Christmas
OL,6,FShopper footfall rallied in January
OL,7,Fcompared with the disappointing
OL,8,FChristmas but remained down on a year
OL,9,Fearlier, figures show.
OL,11,FAlthough shopper visits across the UK
OL,12,Fas a whole were down 0.6% on last
OL,13,FJanuary, this was an improvement on
OL,14,Fthe 2.9% decline seen in December,
OL,15,Faccording to British Retail Consortium
OL,16,F(BRC)-Sensormatic data.
