OL,3,CShopper footfall down on last January
OL,4,Cbut up on disappointing Christmas
OL,6,FHigh street visits fell by a steeper
OL,7,F1.9% year-on-year in January, down
OL,8,Ffrom the 0.9% drop seen in December,
OL,9,Fwhile shopping centre footfall fell by
OL,10,F0.8% in January but improved from the
OL,11,F5.1% plunge over Christmas.
OL,13,FThe best performing cities were in the
OL,14,Fnorth, where shopper traffic was hit
OL,15,Fbadly by severe storms last year, and
OL,16,Fretail parks also recorded positive
OL,17,Fgrowth as customers made the most of
OL,18,Ffree parking to shop in person during
OL,19,Fthe January sales.
