OL,3,CShopper footfall down on last January
OL,4,Cbut up on disappointing Christmas
OL,6,FScotland recorded the strongest year-
OL,7,Fon-year growth in footfall, up 5.1%,
OL,8,Fwith Northern Ireland also seeing
OL,9,Fsignificant growth of 3.8%.
OL,11,FBy contrast, footfall fell across the
OL,12,Frest of the UK ` by 1.4% in England
OL,13,Fand 2.8% in Wales.
OL,15,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,16,Fsaid: "Although footfall edged down in
OL,17,FJanuary compared to a year earlier, it
OL,18,Fwas much better than the disappointing
OL,19,FChristmas period.
