OL,6,F"An uptick in consumer confidence and
OL,7,Fpossible signs of a footfall recovery
OL,8,Foffer some cautious optimism for some
OL,9,Fspring-like green shoots."
OL,11,FAndy Sumpter from Sensormatic said:
OL,12,F"January offered a welcome reset for
OL,13,FUK retail, with footfall recording its
OL,14,Fbest performance in five months.
OL,16,F"Some of this uplift will have been
OL,17,Fdriven by savvier spending behaviours,
OL,18,Fas consumers took advantage of new
OL,19,Fyear promotions and sought out value
OL,20,Fafter a stretched festive period.
